news.title: New circle rates for FY23 comes into effect in Ghaziabad
news.para: The average hike in circle rates as compared to last time is between 10% and 12% but it has increased by up to 20% in some areas.

news.title: Ahmedabad: Luxury bungalow owners of 50-hectare scheme to get BU nod after a decade
news.para: The inquiry committee was to investigate if there were irregularities in giving plan approvals and building use (BU) permissions to individual bungalows and if the exemption from deducting 40% land from the 50-hectare plot for common services was valid.

news.title: Chennai: IndiQube leases 1.5 lakh sq ft office space in Ekkattuthangal
news.para: IndiQube, has leased over 1.5 lakh sq ft of property, where a G+11 Multi-Storey Building (MSB) is under construction. The structure with a capacity of more than 3,000 seats is likely operational by February, 2023.

news.title: Yes Bank-DHFL: CBI seeks to attach Rs 600 crore foreign assets
news.para: The prosecution also pressed for interim attachment of properties. The special CBI court is likely to hear the matter on August 26.

news.title: Not a single brick can be laid without police & authorities collusion: SC
news.para: It said when an officer changes, no one accepts the responsibility and they will say it happened during the previous officer's tenure. And this internal arrangement works quite fine.

news.title: Property tax rates in Delhi likely to go up marginally
news.para: The civic body also issued a statement saying the base unit area values were recommended by the first MVC in 2004 which has remained unchanged for the last 18 years.

news.title: Gurugram: CAQM notice to Pivotal Devaan for use of diesel gensets
news.para: Pivotal Infrastructure Pvt Ltd had applied for a connection with a load of 2,736.5kW in May 2019 for the society, but DHBVN hasn’t approved it yet as the developer hasn’t submitted the required documents.

news.title: Adani Good Homes ready to change bid condition for Radius Estates
news.para: ICICI Prudential VC Fund had argued that the condition was in violation of the original bidding terms which had provided for all such recoveries of bad debts to be distributed amongst the company's creditors.

news.title: Swedish home prices slide again in July as economic gloom deepens
news.para: Home prices fell 2.9% month-on-month, figures from Valueguard's HOX Index showed, while prices were down 2.6% from the same month in 2021.

news.title: China probes state property firm executives for 'serious violations'
news.para: Authorities said in separate notices on Tuesday that they were investigating Zhuang Yuekai, chairman of C&D Real Estate, and Shi Zhen, chairman of C&D Urban Services.

news.title: Chandigarh civic body to auction 18 commercial properties
news.para: The civic body has estimated Rs 61.71 crore as reserve price for the properties, varying from over Rs 3 crore to Rs 6 crore for each as per size, location and other criteria.

news.title: Indore civic body seals nine commercial outlets
news.para: Three establishments of Bicholi Mardana area including two food outlets and an automobile service station were sealed for operating without completion certificates.

news.title: Mumbai: Three weak buildings around crashed Borivli house demolished
news.para: Gitanjali building, over four decades old, crashed on the afternoon of August 19 but fortunately nobody was injured as the residents had run out after feeling tremors.

news.title: Omkar Group promoters discharged in money laundering case
news.para: Earlier this month, the accused moved discharge pleas before the special PMLA court through their advocates Vijay Aggarwal and Rahul Agarwal.

news.title: Maharashtra housing federation fine with water data share, not fee
